---
title: Ginger Miso Beef Noodle Stir-Fry with Mushrooms and Crispy Onions
description: Looking for a super quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Ginger Miso Beef Udon Stir-Fry in just 15 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
